`,n.jsx(e.h2,{children:"About the Institute"}),`
`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"IIT Goa operates in Ponda, Goa, giving interns access to regional industries and research ecosystems. The campus hosts active centers spanning AI/ML and computing, Power and energy, Materials and manufacturing and collaborates with government and industry sponsors. If you are comparing across the IIT system, anchor your choices with the IIT internships hub to see where this institute leads on depth, facilities, and sponsored work."}),`
